# ==============================================================================
# RECALL - LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (.env.local.example)
# ==============================================================================
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file to '.env.local' (gitignored by default).
# 2. Update these dummy values with your actual developer keys/endpoints.
# 3. WARNING: Never use production keys (especially FERNET_KEY and JWT_SECRET) here.
# ==============================================================================

# --- DATABASE (Neon Development Branch) ---
# MUST contain "dev" or "test" in the string to satisfy dev_seed.py protection.
